dct_title_s: Empire d'Ethiopie, colonies européennes du littoral et partie du Soudan Egyptien
dct_description_sm: Map of Empire of Ethiopia, Italian Somaliland, British Somaliland, and Egyptian Sudan, showing actual and proposed railway lines and telegraph lines. Relief shown by contour lines.

dct_publisher_sm: [Paris] : Service géographique du Ministère des affaires etrangères, 1907.
